          "_name": "people04",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"people04\" plugins=\"Masonry\" group=\"People\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\t<mbr-parameters>\n\t\t<header>Size</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n\t\t<header>Show/Hide</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\">\n\t\t<header>Card</header>\n\t\t<select title=\"Columns\" name=\"columns\">\n\t\t\t<option value=\"12\">1</option>\n\t\t\t<option value=\"6\">2</option>\n\t\t\t<option value=\"4\" selected>3</option>\n\t\t\t<option value=\"3\">4</option>\n\t\t</select>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Image\" name=\"showImage\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Name\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n\t\t<header>Background</header>\n\t\t<fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffd7ef\" selected>\n\t\t</fieldset>\n\t\t\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t</mbr-parameters>\n\t<div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n\t</div>\n\t<div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row mb-5 justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-12 mb-0 content-head\">\n\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<b>Testimoni</b></h3>\n\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n\t\t\t\t\tList your customers' testimonials in this block.</h5>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"row mbr-masonry\" data-masonry=\"{&quot;percentPosition&quot;: true }\">\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} active\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">\"Saya merasa jauh lebih kuat dan percaya diri setelah mengikuti sesi konsultasi di sini. Konselornya sangat ramah dan solutif, saya merasa lebih optimis menjalani hidup.\"</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper mt-4 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-160x107.jpg\" data-slide-to=\"2\" data-bs-slide-to=\"2\" alt>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\"><b>Ayu</b><b><br></b><b>25 tahun</b></h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">\"Setelah beberapa kali mengikuti sesi konsultasi di Sahabat Puan, saya merasakan perubahan besar dalam cara pandang saya terhadap diri sendiri. Mereka sangat mengerti apa yang saya butuhkan.\"</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper mt-4 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-160x90.jpg\" data-slide-to=\"3\" data-bs-slide-to=\"3\" alt>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\"><b>Vania </b><br><b>30 tahun</b></h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">\"Saya merasa jauh lebih kuat dan percaya diri setelah mengikuti sesi konsultasi di sini. Konselornya sangat ramah dan solutif, saya merasa lebih optimis menjalani hidup.\"</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img-wrapper mt-4 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-160x160.jpg\" data-slide-to=\"4\" data-bs-slide-to=\"4\" alt>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\"><b>Karin </b><br><b>19 tahun</b></h5>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</section>",
